未成年人。坚持依法惩戒和精准帮教相结合，准确甄别未成年人在网络犯罪中的地位、作用，采取更有针对性的处置措施，提升教育感化挽救工作实效。对于情节严重的犯罪，坚决依法惩治，让涉罪未成年人充分感受法治威严。2020 年至 2022 年，检察机关起诉未成年人涉嫌利用电信网络实施犯罪 7221 人。对于主观恶性不大、罪行较轻、属于初犯、偶犯、有积极悔改表现的未成年人，在依法从轻处理的同时，「宽容不纵容、严管又厚爱」。2020 年至 2022 年，检察机关对涉嫌帮助信息网络犯罪活动罪的未成年人依法适用附条件不起诉 2749 人最高检：依法严惩「隔空猥亵」等侵害未成年人犯罪 _ 法治中国 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604031386"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIpeHahPnslI4KEAMaCDk2NTA5Mzg3IIT126MGMAE4HUArcgk2MDQwMzEzODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1685607005.4666197", "card_id": "Q_604133278", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 224}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年 618，有哪些微单相机值得推荐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-05fab83ac7bc82141ef3319586dfb0fc_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604133278"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpeHahPnslI4KEAMaCDk2NTMyMDQyIMXH3aMGMAA4/wFALHIJNjA0MTMzMjc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1685607005.467165", "card_id": "Q_604184178", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 14}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "5 月财新中国制造业 PMI 录得 50.9 ，时隔两个月重回扩张区间，如何解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月财新中国制造业 PMI 升至 50.9 时隔两个月重回扩张区间 6 月 1 日公布的 5 月财新中国制造业采购经理指数（PMI）录得 50.9，较 4 月回升 1.4 个百分点，时隔两个月重回扩张区间。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": 